                     <interp inst="t17890909-143-person1242" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner put his hand into the window, and take out the cotton.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of it.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness to his character.</p>
